00:37:58.470 --> 00:38:01.515
or maybe I should say,
high-energy collisions.

00:38:05.594 --> 00:38:09.560
We will, of course, talk about
nanokelvin collisions, which

00:38:09.560 --> 00:38:11.290
is the physics of
the scattering links

00:38:11.290 --> 00:38:13.830
and some s-wave collisions
which are really

00:38:13.830 --> 00:38:15.950
