quantum gases.

00:38:20.050 --> 00:38:23.120
We're not talking about
any advanced topic

00:38:23.120 --> 00:38:24.015
in atomic structure.

00:38:26.910 --> 00:38:30.630
All we do about atomic
structure is done in 8.421.

00:38:30.630 --> 00:38:34.980
And if you want to graduate
in atomic physics at MIT,

00:38:34.980 --> 00:38:37.890
